examples.en: John is in the seventh grade.
The boxer was flattened in the seventh round.
Only about a seventh of the town voted for her.
The patient is a gravid woman in her seventh month.
She is now seventh in line of succession to the throne.
She has only a vague recollection of her seventh birthday party.
Greg stared down from the seventh floor and began to feel giddy.
I'm planning to leave on the seventh (=the seventh day of the month).
My regiment was brigaded with the Sixth, Seventh, and Eighth Regiments.
In his sixty-seventh year his heart cut didoes. *
I lost my wad on a rotten horse in the seventh race. *
The other time I was riding the Seventh Avenue with my week's rip in a large expensive suitcase. *
